{
  "version": 1,
  "cells": [
    {
      "kind": "markdown",
      "value": "# Facet Notebook — Kernel Demo\n\nPress **⇧↩** to evaluate. The **Facet IR** pipeline parses expressions, then a **SymPy kernel** computes the result and renders it as LaTeX.\n\n**Kernel directives** — type in any code cell and run:\n\n| Directive | Effect |\n|---|---|\n| `%init(sympy, name=\"k\")` | Start a local SymPy kernel named `k` |\n| `%init(remote, name=\"k\", url=\"http://host:8765\")` | Connect to a remote HTTP kernel |\n| `%use(k)` | Switch the active kernel to `k` |\n| `%restart(k)` | Kill and re-warm kernel `k` |\n| `%kill(k)` | Remove kernel `k` |\n| `%kernels()` | List all running kernels |\n| `%clear(name?)` | Clear one or all session variables |\n\nThe **Command Palette** (`Facet:`) offers the same operations interactively. The status bar (bottom-right) shows the active kernel.",
      "readMode": "surface"
    },
    {
      "kind": "markdown",
      "value": "## 1 · Integration",
      "readMode": "surface"
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "value": "I := int[x : 0..inf](exp(-x^2))",
      "readMode": "surface",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "mime": "application/x-facet-expression",
          "data": "{\n\t\"source\": \"I := int[x : 0..inf](exp(-x^2))\",\n\t\"readMode\": \"surface\",\n\t\"results\": {\n\t\t\"surface\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"I := int[x : 0..inf](exp(-x ^ 2))\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"strict\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \":=(I, int(binder(x, range(0, inf)), exp(^(neg(x), 2))))\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"core\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"(:= I (int (binder x (range 0 inf)) (exp (^ (neg x) 2))))\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"object\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"{\\\"head\\\":\\\":=\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"I\\\"},{\\\"head\\\":\\\"int\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"binder\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"},{\\\"head\\\":\\\"range\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"int\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"0\\\"},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"inf\\\"}]}]},{\\\"head\\\":\\\"exp\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"^\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"neg\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"}]},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"int\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"2\\\"}]}]}]}]}\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"latex\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"I := \\\\int_{0}^{\\\\infty} \\\\operatorname{exp}\\\\left(-x^{2}\\\\right)\\\\,dx\"\n\t\t}\n\t},\n\t\"kernel\": {\n\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\"latex\": \"\\\\frac{1}{2} \\\\pi^{\\\\frac{1}{2}}\",\n\t\t\"core\": \"(* (/ 1 2) (^ pi (/ 1 2)))\",\n\t\t\"assignName\": \"I\"\n\t}\n}"
        },
        {
          "mime": "text/plain",
          "data": "\\frac{1}{2} \\pi^{\\frac{1}{2}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "value": "I^2",
      "readMode": "surface",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "mime": "application/x-facet-expression",
          "data": "{\n\t\"source\": \"I^2\",\n\t\"readMode\": \"surface\",\n\t\"results\": {\n\t\t\"surface\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"I ^ 2\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"strict\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"^(I, 2)\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"core\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"(^ I 2)\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"object\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"{\\\"head\\\":\\\"^\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"I\\\"},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"int\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"2\\\"}]}\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"latex\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"I^{2}\"\n\t\t}\n\t},\n\t\"kernel\": {\n\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\"latex\": \"\\\\frac{1}{4} \\\\pi\",\n\t\t\"core\": \"(* (/ 1 4) pi)\"\n\t}\n}"
        },
        {
          "mime": "text/plain",
          "data": "\\frac{1}{4} \\pi"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "value": "sum[k : 1..inf](1/k^2)",
      "readMode": "surface",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "mime": "application/x-facet-expression",
          "data": "{\n\t\"source\": \"sum[k : 1..inf](1/k^2)\",\n\t\"readMode\": \"surface\",\n\t\"results\": {\n\t\t\"surface\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"sum[k : 1..inf](1 / k ^ 2)\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"strict\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"sum(binder(k, range(1, inf)), /(1, ^(k, 2)))\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"core\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"(sum (binder k (range 1 inf)) (/ 1 (^ k 2)))\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"object\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"{\\\"head\\\":\\\"sum\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"binder\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"k\\\"},{\\\"head\\\":\\\"range\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"int\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"1\\\"},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"inf\\\"}]}]},{\\\"head\\\":\\\"/\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"int\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"1\\\"},{\\\"head\\\":\\\"^\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"k\\\"},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"int\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"2\\\"}]}]}]}\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"latex\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"\\\\sum_{k = 1}^{\\\\infty} \\\\frac{1}{k^{2}}\"\n\t\t}\n\t},\n\t\"kernel\": {\n\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\"latex\": \"\\\\frac{1}{6} \\\\pi^{2}\",\n\t\t\"core\": \"(* (/ 1 6) (^ pi 2))\"\n\t}\n}"
        },
        {
          "mime": "text/plain",
          "data": "\\frac{1}{6} \\pi^{2}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "value": "int[x : 0..pi](sin(x))",
      "readMode": "surface",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "mime": "application/x-facet-expression",
          "data": "{\n\t\"source\": \"int[x : 0..pi](sin(x))\",\n\t\"readMode\": \"surface\",\n\t\"results\": {\n\t\t\"surface\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"int[x : 0..pi](sin(x))\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"strict\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"int(binder(x, range(0, pi)), sin(x))\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"core\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"(int (binder x (range 0 pi)) (sin x))\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"object\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"{\\\"head\\\":\\\"int\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"binder\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"},{\\\"head\\\":\\\"range\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"int\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"0\\\"},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"pi\\\"}]}]},{\\\"head\\\":\\\"sin\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"}]}]}\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"latex\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"\\\\int_{0}^{\\\\pi} \\\\sin\\\\left(x\\\\right)\\\\,dx\"\n\t\t}\n\t},\n\t\"kernel\": {\n\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\"latex\": \"2\",\n\t\t\"core\": \"2\"\n\t}\n}"
        },
        {
          "mime": "text/plain",
          "data": "2"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "markdown",
      "value": "## 2 · Differentiation",
      "readMode": "surface"
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "value": "diff[x](sin(x)^2)",
      "readMode": "surface",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "mime": "application/x-facet-expression",
          "data": "{\n\t\"source\": \"diff[x](sin(x)^2)\",\n\t\"readMode\": \"surface\",\n\t\"results\": {\n\t\t\"surface\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"diff[x](sin(x) ^ 2)\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"strict\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"diff(^(sin(x), 2), x)\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"core\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"(diff (^ (sin x) 2) x)\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"object\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"{\\\"head\\\":\\\"diff\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"^\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"sin\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"}]},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"int\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"2\\\"}]},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"}]}\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"latex\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"\\\\frac{d^{}}{dx} \\\\sin\\\\left(x\\\\right)^{2}\"\n\t\t}\n\t},\n\t\"kernel\": {\n\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\"latex\": \"2 \\\\sin\\\\left(x\\\\right) \\\\cos\\\\left(x\\\\right)\",\n\t\t\"core\": \"(* (* 2 (sin x)) (cos x))\"\n\t}\n}"
        },
        {
          "mime": "text/plain",
          "data": "2 \\sin\\left(x\\right) \\cos\\left(x\\right)"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "value": "diff[x, x, x,x](exp(-x^2))",
      "readMode": "surface",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "mime": "application/x-facet-expression",
          "data": "{\n\t\"source\": \"diff[x, x, x,x](exp(-x^2))\",\n\t\"readMode\": \"surface\",\n\t\"results\": {\n\t\t\"surface\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"diff[x, x, x, x](exp(-x ^ 2))\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"strict\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"diff(exp(^(neg(x), 2)), x, x, x, x)\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"core\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"(diff (exp (^ (neg x) 2)) x x x x)\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"object\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"{\\\"head\\\":\\\"diff\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"exp\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"^\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"neg\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"}]},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"int\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"2\\\"}]}]},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"}]}\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"latex\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"\\\\frac{d^{}^{}^{}^{}}{dxdxdxdx} \\\\operatorname{exp}\\\\left(-x^{2}\\\\right)\"\n\t\t}\n\t},\n\t\"kernel\": {\n\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\"latex\": \"4 \\\\left(4 x^{4} + -1 12 x^{2} + 3\\\\right) \\\\operatorname{exp}\\\\left(-x^{2}\\\\right)\",\n\t\t\"core\": \"(* (* 4 (+ (+ (* 4 (^ x 4)) (* (* -1 12) (^ x 2))) 3)) (exp (neg (^ x 2))))\"\n\t}\n}"
        },
        {
          "mime": "text/plain",
          "data": "4 \\left(4 x^{4} + -1 12 x^{2} + 3\\right) \\operatorname{exp}\\left(-x^{2}\\right)"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "value": "simplify(sin(x)^2 + cos(x)^2)",
      "readMode": "surface",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "mime": "application/x-facet-expression",
          "data": "{\n\t\"source\": \"simplify(sin(x)^2 + cos(x)^2)\",\n\t\"readMode\": \"surface\",\n\t\"results\": {\n\t\t\"surface\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"simplify(sin(x) ^ 2 + cos(x) ^ 2)\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"strict\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"simplify(+(^(sin(x), 2), ^(cos(x), 2)))\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"core\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"(simplify (+ (^ (sin x) 2) (^ (cos x) 2)))\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"object\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"{\\\"head\\\":\\\"simplify\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"+\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"^\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"sin\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"}]},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"int\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"2\\\"}]},{\\\"head\\\":\\\"^\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"cos\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"}]},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"int\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"2\\\"}]}]}]}\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"latex\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"\\\\operatorname{simplify}\\\\left(\\\\sin\\\\left(x\\\\right)^{2} + \\\\cos\\\\left(x\\\\right)^{2}\\\\right)\"\n\t\t}\n\t},\n\t\"kernel\": {\n\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\"latex\": \"1\",\n\t\t\"core\": \"1\"\n\t}\n}"
        },
        {
          "mime": "text/plain",
          "data": "1"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "markdown",
      "value": "## 3 · Limits & session variables\n\n`:=` evaluates the RHS and binds the result to a name for subsequent cells. `I^2` in Section 1 uses `I` defined two cells above it.",
      "readMode": "surface"
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "value": "lim[x -> 0](sin(x)/x)",
      "readMode": "surface",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "mime": "application/x-facet-expression",
          "data": "{\n\t\"source\": \"lim[x -> 0](sin(x)/x)\",\n\t\"readMode\": \"surface\",\n\t\"results\": {\n\t\t\"surface\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"lim[x -> 0](sin(x) / x)\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"strict\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"lim(binder(x, approach(0)), /(sin(x), x))\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"core\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"(lim (binder x (approach 0)) (/ (sin x) x))\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"object\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"{\\\"head\\\":\\\"lim\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"binder\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"},{\\\"head\\\":\\\"approach\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"int\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"0\\\"}]}]},{\\\"head\\\":\\\"/\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"sin\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"}]},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"}]}]}\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"latex\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"\\\\lim_{x \\\\to 0} \\\\frac{\\\\sin\\\\left(x\\\\right)}{x}\"\n\t\t}\n\t},\n\t\"kernel\": {\n\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\"latex\": \"1\",\n\t\t\"core\": \"1\"\n\t}\n}"
        },
        {
          "mime": "text/plain",
          "data": "1"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "markdown",
      "value": "## 4 · Multiple kernels\n\nSeveral independent SymPy processes can run simultaneously. The cells below walk through the full lifecycle: init → switch → compute → restart → compute again → inspect → switch back.",
      "readMode": "surface"
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "value": "%init(sympy, name=\"local2\")",
      "readMode": "surface",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "mime": "text/plain",
          "data": "Kernel 'local2' initialized [sympy]"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "value": "%use(local2)",
      "readMode": "surface",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "mime": "text/plain",
          "data": "Active kernel → local2"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "value": "diff[x, x](exp(-x^2))",
      "readMode": "surface",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "mime": "application/x-facet-expression",
          "data": "{\n\t\"source\": \"diff[x, x](exp(-x^2))\",\n\t\"readMode\": \"surface\",\n\t\"results\": {\n\t\t\"surface\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"diff[x, x](exp(-x ^ 2))\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"strict\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"diff(exp(^(neg(x), 2)), x, x)\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"core\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"(diff (exp (^ (neg x) 2)) x x)\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"object\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"{\\\"head\\\":\\\"diff\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"exp\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"^\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"neg\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"}]},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"int\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"2\\\"}]}]},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"}]}\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"latex\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"\\\\frac{d^{}^{}}{dxdx} \\\\operatorname{exp}\\\\left(-x^{2}\\\\right)\"\n\t\t}\n\t},\n\t\"kernel\": {\n\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\"latex\": \"2 \\\\left(2 x^{2} - 1\\\\right) \\\\operatorname{exp}\\\\left(-x^{2}\\\\right)\",\n\t\t\"core\": \"(* (* 2 (+ (* 2 (^ x 2)) -1)) (exp (neg (^ x 2))))\"\n\t}\n}"
        },
        {
          "mime": "text/plain",
          "data": "2 \\left(2 x^{2} - 1\\right) \\operatorname{exp}\\left(-x^{2}\\right)"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "value": "%restart(local2)",
      "readMode": "surface",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "mime": "text/plain",
          "data": "Kernel 'local2' restarted"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "value": "diff[x, x](exp(-x^2))",
      "readMode": "surface",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "mime": "application/x-facet-expression",
          "data": "{\n\t\"source\": \"diff[x, x](exp(-x^2))\",\n\t\"readMode\": \"surface\",\n\t\"results\": {\n\t\t\"surface\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"diff[x, x](exp(-x ^ 2))\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"strict\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"diff(exp(^(neg(x), 2)), x, x)\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"core\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"(diff (exp (^ (neg x) 2)) x x)\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"object\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"{\\\"head\\\":\\\"diff\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"exp\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"^\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"head\\\":\\\"neg\\\",\\\"args\\\":[{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"}]},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"int\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"2\\\"}]}]},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"},{\\\"atom\\\":\\\"sym\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"x\\\"}]}\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t\"latex\": {\n\t\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\t\"text\": \"\\\\frac{d^{}^{}}{dxdx} \\\\operatorname{exp}\\\\left(-x^{2}\\\\right)\"\n\t\t}\n\t},\n\t\"kernel\": {\n\t\t\"ok\": true,\n\t\t\"latex\": \"2 \\\\left(2 x^{2} - 1\\\\right) \\\\operatorname{exp}\\\\left(-x^{2}\\\\right)\",\n\t\t\"core\": \"(* (* 2 (+ (* 2 (^ x 2)) -1)) (exp (neg (^ x 2))))\"\n\t}\n}"
        },
        {
          "mime": "text/plain",
          "data": "2 \\left(2 x^{2} - 1\\right) \\operatorname{exp}\\left(-x^{2}\\right)"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "value": "%kernels()",
      "readMode": "surface",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "mime": "text/plain",
          "data": "  sympy [sympy]\n▶ local2 [sympy]"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "value": "%use(sympy)",
      "readMode": "surface",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "mime": "text/plain",
          "data": "Active kernel → sympy"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "markdown",
      "value": "## 5 · Remote kernels\n\nA kernel can run on any machine with Python + SymPy. Start the server anywhere:\n\n```bash\npip install sympy\npython3 nbs/kernel_server.py --port 8765\n```\n\nThe cells below connect to it, compute the Basel sum remotely, then clean up. Free-tier options: Oracle Cloud always-free ARM VM, fly.io, Railway, GitHub Codespaces.",
      "readMode": "surface"
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "value": "%init(remote, name=\"remote-sympy\", url=\"http://localhost:8765\")",
      "readMode": "surface",
      "outputs": [
